LineComment.Text:
For every alarm that should appear in the HMI, it has to be translated into WinCC's alarm format This is a very "dumb" way to do it, but the advantage is it's easy to understand and easy to modify.
Steps to add a new alarm: 1. Add an entry in DB_WinCCAlarms under the right category 2. Add a network in this FC with a WinCCAlarm block 3. In the WinCC project, import the tag from DB_WinCCAlarms 4. In the WinCC project, create an alarm which references this tag
